data.description: Charming Home with Great Potential! This delightful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom house is a perfect canvas for someone looking to add their personal touch. Located in a quiet neighborhood, this property offers a blend of convenience and tranquility. Key Features include: spacious living room with abundant natural light, cozy fireplace in the family room for chilly evenings, a large kitchen perfect for entertaining, a private backyard with potential for landscaping and outdoor entertainment, 2.5 car attached garage with ample storage space, conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers. Cosmetic Opportunities include: you can update the kitchen and bathrooms to modernize the home, or refresh paint and flooring to suit your style, or enhance curb appeal with landscaping and exterior updates. Do some or all of these and you will have the perfect home. Updates already taken care of for you include: a new hot water heater(2023), newer roof and gutters(2023), stainless steel appliances(2022), HVAC new in 2011 and the home is wired for an alarm system.  Home is being sold as-is, but with a bit of TLC and creative vision, this house can be transformed into your dream home. Don't miss this opportunity to make it your own!
